    <item>
      <title>世界领导人缅怀参议员林赛·格雷厄姆</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-world-react.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格雷厄姆周六突然去世，引发了人们对这位二十年来在美国外交政策中影响巨大且常常造成分裂的人物的哀悼浪潮。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-world-react.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 13:12:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>共和党参议员、特朗普的坚定盟友林赛·格雷厄姆死于“突发疾病”</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-dead.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[他的办公室称，他于周六晚上因“短暂而突然的疾病”去世。在参议院任职的二十多年来，他始终致力于推动美国在海外使用军事力量。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-dead.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 13:10:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林赛·格雷厄姆 (Lindsey Graham) 将于 11 月面临连任。现在发生了什么？</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-reelection-seat.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南卡罗来纳州的法律规定，他的去世将引发 8 月 11 日举行的特别共和党初选，该州州长可以任命一名继任者，完成其剩余任期，直至 1 月初。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/07/12/us/politics/lindsey-graham-death-reelection-seat.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Sun, 12 Jul 2026 12:54:01 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
